    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056520/extras/492908d00aebb4e2b13dea2806304f2d.poster.avif?t=1753789943\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056520/extras/492908d00aebb4e2b13dea2806304f2d.webm?t=1753789943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056520/extras/492908d00aebb4e2b13dea2806304f2d.mp4?t=1753789943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>击败成群的月之怪物，努力生存下去！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Moonbane Survivor》是一款Roguelite角色扮演弹幕射击游戏，背景设定在被月亮神秘力量摧毁的城市中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败敌人、收集战利品、构建你的专属流派，不断变强。为了拯救这个世界而战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>通过独特的武器模块与装备组合，在弹幕中穿梭，体验惊险刺激的生存快感！</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >消灭无尽的敌人浪潮</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集战利品，装备新道具来提升实力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组合多种武器模块，打造属于你的强大武器库</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攻克关卡，解锁全新武器与模块</p></li></ul>",
